game.name: Parking Panic
game.description:
Everyone is out there in the market to purchase gifts for Christmas so most of the parking lots seem to be crowded. Only expert drivers can park their vehicles on the given places. Do you think that you have the ability to park like an expert driver? Join Parking Panic and be prepared to find a way to get your car out of a totally crowded parking lot! Try to move your cars, buses and trailers and make sure to get it parked while avoiding all the obstacles!

Be careful since this a rush hour and every car owner wants to find out a right parking place in this HTML5 parking game! Take your seat in your red car and get ready to find a way to get out of your parking spot! There is no need to bother in case of being surrounded by other vehicles of varying sizes. Test your parking and driving abilities to move cars and buses that want to block you and restrict you from reaching up a path to the exit!

Your objective in this one of the best car games is to move your red color car to the exit. Use your mouse or tap the screen to move any vehicle! Put your fingers on your mouse to click and drag your vehicle forward or backward! There are 100 unique and challenging levels to play through, and 300 stars to collect.  All the best to complete levels to secure all stars to become the best car parking champion!
